query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(k mk t mi) */ select min(t.title) AS movie_title
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword like '%sequel%'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1996
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('American',
'Norway',
'Denish',
'Denmark',
'USA',
'America',
'Bulgaria',
'Germany');
